    <h1>EX&#xAD;PRESS TREAT&#xAD;MENTS AT CLARINS SPA BOU&#xAD;TIQUES</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201225/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-12-25"><time>2020-12-25</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE STYLE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>Want a quick skin fix? Clarins has tai­lored ex­press fa­cial treat­ments for the time-strapped, con­dens­ing the ben­e­fits of the French brand’s pro­fes­sional treat­ments into half-hour ses­sions.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at Clarins bou­tiques at West­gate, Plaza Sin­ga­pura and BHG Bugis, the ses­sions com­prise a 10-minute skin con­sul­ta­tion, fol­lowed by a 20-minute treat­ment us­ing Clarins prod­ucts. The counter at BHG Bugis is the brand’s first to of­fer its Open Spa ser­vices.</p>
    <p>Choose from a range of bright­en­ing, pu­ri­fy­ing, and re­ju­ve­nat­ing treat­ments – such as Bye Dry Skin, SOS Detox (to help skin re­gain ra­di­ance), SOS V-Shape (to lift and firm fa­cial con­tours), and Skin En­er­gizer for Men (a tar­geted treat­ment for guys to re­store vi­tal­ity and tone the skin). Treat­ments are $38 each.</p>
    <p>Info: Clarins Ex­press Treat­ments are avail­able at BHG Bugis, Bugis Junc­tion, 200 Vic­to­ria Street; 01-26 West­gate, 3 Gate­way Drive; and B1-05 Plaza Sin­ga­pura, 68 Or­chard Road</p>

